inlineContent.text: Thrown when you attempt to use the SDK from any thread not main
Thrown when you attempt to use the SDK prior to initialising it
Thrown when you attempt to use playback controls when AutomixIQ is not on
Thrown when you attempt to turn on AutomixIQ but it is already on
Thrown when you attempt to load an empty playlist
Thrown when you attempt to insert a track at a position outside the bounds of the loaded playlist
Thrown when the metadata for a track you are trying to load is not available and could not be downloaded
Thrown when AutomixIQ fails internally (not user error)
Thrown when you attempt to remove a track at a position outside the bounds of the loaded playlist
Thrown when you attempt to play but AutomixIQ is already playing
Thrown when you attempt to pause but AutomixIQ is already paused
Thrown when you attempt to go to the previous track but AutomixIQ is already on the first in the playlist and “Repeat” is off
Thrown when you attempt to go to the next track but AutomixIQ is already on the last in the playlist and “Repeat” is off
Thrown when you attempt to go to the start of a track but the playlist is empty
Thrown when you attempt to seek to a track but the playlist is empty or the index is out of bounds of the playlist
Thrown when you attempt to seek within a track but the playlist is empty or the track is not yet loaded
Thrown when you attempt to move a track that is not on the loaded playlist
Thrown when you attempt to select a track to be played until the end but that track is not on the loaded playlist
Thrown when you attempt to move a track at a position outside the bounds of the loaded playlist
Thrown when you attempt to stop looping a track but that track is not on the loaded playlist
Thrown when you attempt to loop a track but that track is not on the loaded playlist
Thrown when you attempt to use an unimplemented method of the SDK
Thrown when an action you previously issued to AutomixIQ is cancelled due to another user initialed action that overrides it
Thrown when you attempt to turn AutomixIQ on while it is already turning on
Thrown when you attempt to turn AutomixIQ on while it is already turning off
Thrown when you attempt to turn AutomixIQ off while it is already turning off
Thrown when you attempt to turn AutomixIQ off while it is already turning on
Thrown when AutomixIQ fails to set up the channel layout
Thrown when AutomixIQ fails to set up the input buffer
Thrown when AutomixIQ fails to set up the AVAudioSession
Thrown when AutomixIQ fails to start the audio engine
Thrown when AutomixIQ fails to restore the audio session to the state it found it when you turned it on
Thrown when AutomixIQ is unable to be stopped
Thrown when you attempt to load an explicit track but the setting to filter out explicit tracks is on
Thrown when you fail to download the ad from the url provided
Thrown when you attempt to do something you cannot do while playing an ad
